data.description: OWNED solar and sparkling pebble tec pool w/ water features! This home's versatility has appeal to buyers looking for almost any living accommodation. Welcome to this 3800+ SF Granville built estate- downstairs features an updated kitchen leading into the family room, a living room across from a formal dining, bedroom & full bath PLUS a bonus room which can function as a game room, dedicated multi-gen living room, office, gym, 5th bedroom or any other purpose that suits your families needs. Upstairs, you encounter 2 more bedrooms, a newly remodeled full bathroom & a flex' room.  Across the landing, on its own wing, is the master suite, complete with a coffee bar, spa-like bathroom, his & her closets & a balcony overlooking the pool. Out front you are welcomed home by a brand new custom front door, 3 car garage, plenty of driveway space & mature landscaping. Back inside, you cannot escape the abundance of natural light shining down across the vaulted ceiling. There are also multiple exterior access points that allow seamless indoor/outdoor living. When it's time to wind down, the functional floor plan allows everyone in the family to have their own interior retreat. Entertainment? Individual space? Multi-gen living? Work from home? Gym? All options! Can't forget water softening system & whole house fan! Close to parks and walking trails!
